main_body:
Decision 2000/185/EC is hereby amended as follows:
1. in the first subparagraph of Article 1 "three years running from 1 January 2000 to 31 December 2002" shall be replaced by "four years running from 1 January 2000 to 31 December 2003";
2. in the second subparagraph of Article 3, "31 December 2002" shall be replaced by "31 December 2003".
